h3. Ingredients

* 2kg spare ribs
* 2 medium onions, sliced
* 2 teaspoons vinegar
* 2 teaspoons Worcestershire sauce
* 1 teaspoon salt
* 1 teaspoon Hungarian paprika
* 1/4 to 1/2 teaspoon ground cayenne pepper
* 1/2 teaspoon ground black pepper
* 1 teaspoon chili powder
* 3/4 cup ketchup
* 3/4 cup water

h3. Preperation

* Cut racks into serving-size pieces. 
* Sprinkle spareribs with salt and pepper. 
* Place in roaster pan; cover with onions. 
* Combine remaining ingredients; pour over ribs. 
* Cover pan with foil and bake at 180 Â° for about 1 1/2 hours. Baste occasionally and turn spareribs a few times. Remove cover last 15 minutes to brown ribs. 

Serves 4 to 6.
